Ban comand:
?ban {username / ID} {reason}

Reasons to ban a user:
repeated violation of the rules
n word / bypass
nazi words

Profile contents:
Username - bannable
Nicknames - bannable
Profilepictures - bannable
Pronouns - not bannable
Banners - not bannable 
Bio - not bannable

... however you can ban users for their banner / bio / pronouns if they contain extremely controversial topics. 
